Key Match Events: Shohei Ohtani singled in the go-ahead run before stealing his 56th base of the season in the sixth inning
Fernando Tatis Jr. homered to left center (448 feet) in the fifth inning
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was played at Dodger Stadium in Los Angeles, California, with an attendance of 52,310
Others: The Dodgers moved within a victory of clinching the NL West with the win
